    <item>
      <title>ceph在不复制rgw的情况下配置多个区域</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/ceph-configure-multi-regions-without-replicating-rgw/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Jan 2023 18:56:35 +0800</pubDate><author>efim@163.com (starifly)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/ceph-configure-multi-regions-without-replicating-rgw/</guid>
      <category domain="http://localhost:1313/categories/ceph/">ceph</category>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;ceph 在同一个集群配置多个zone，但不同 zone 之间的 rgw 不复制，这种情形应该可以适应多租户环境，因为希望每个租户之间的数据是相互独立的，具体配置可以参考 &lt;a href=&#34;https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_ceph_storage/3/html-single/object_gateway_guide_for_red_hat_enterprise_linux/index#configuring-multiple-zones-without-replication-rgw&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_ceph_storage/3/html-single/object_gateway_guide_for_red_hat_enterprise_linux/index#configuring-multiple-zones-without-replication-rgw&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
